title.narrative: West African Quality System # Support for the implementation of the ECOWAS quality policy

description.narrative: West African Quality System - Support for the implementation of the ECOWAS quality policy (Component 2 of the Support Programme for the Private Sector in West Africa). The overall objective of the Programme is to support the implementation of the regional quality policy of ECOWAS aiming at “establishing a framework for the development and operation of suitable, relevant, efficient and effective quality infrastructures to facilitate intra- regional and internat ional trade, protect the consumer and the environment, and promote sustainable economic development”.
